<center><font size=7><b>Cauldron 1</b></font></center>
<center>Number of entries found: 3</center><p>
<center>
<table width=600>
<TR><TD bgcolor="blue" background=""><font color="white"><b><i>Tips</i></b></font></td></tr>
<TR><TD><a href="http://www.users.globalnet.co.uk/~jimg/yr17/yr17_64.htm">http://www.users.globalnet.co.uk/~jimg/yr17/yr17_64.htm</a>&nbsp; <i>(Unknown in Your Spectrum issue 17)</i> 
<br>
</td></tr>
<TR><TD bgcolor="blue" background=""><font color="white"><b><i>Multiface pokes</i></b></font></td></tr>
<TR><TD><table border="0">
<tr>
<td WIDTH="200" ALIGN="LEFT"><B><U>DESCRIPTION</B></U></TD>
<td WIDTH="200" ALIGN="LEFT"><B><U>POKE(s)</B></U></TD>
</TR>
<tr><td>Infinite Lives</td><td>40060,0</td></tr>
<tr><td>Infinite Hags</td><td>40055,0</td></tr>
<tr><td>Infinite Magic</td><td>28602,0:34756,0</td></tr>
</table>
<BR><ul><B>A couple of points:-</B>
<BR><LI>The HAGS counter goes down, but don't worry.
<LI>You still DIE if you fall off ledges inside buildings - can't be helped.</UL><br>

&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <i>(Gerard Sweeney in Hack Attack III)</i> 
<br>
</td></tr>
<TR><TD bgcolor="blue" background=""><font color="white"><b><i>Type-in hacks</i></b></font></td></tr>
<TR><TD>To obtain infinite lives in Cauldron, wind the tape forward to just past the title screen and type in this program.<br>

&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<br><pre>10 CLEAR 24599: FOR f = 23296 TO 23309: READ a: POKE f,a : NEXT f
20 LET L = USR 23296: POKE 40060,0 : LET L = USR 24600
30 DATA 221,33,24,96,17,2342,159,62,255,55,205,86,5,201</pre><br>

&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<br>Type RUN and restart the tape.
 <i>(Steven Ashford in Sinclair User issue 43)</i> 
<br>
</td></tr>
</table></center><P>
